title: 'Donald Trump doesn't care about Australia' | Daily Mail Online
text: 'Donald Trump doesn't care about Australia': Reporter who broke story of Turnbull's disastrous call with Trump says it shows the President has no time for Australia Malcolm Turnbull refused to deny reportedly hostile talk with Donald Trump Trump reportedly told Turnbull the refugee deal was 'the worst deal ever' President Trump has continued to say he will honour the refugee deal He said the phone conversation was the 'worst call by far' since inauguration Journalist who reported claims said Trump doesn't care about Australia as an ally Published: 04:16 GMT, 2 February 2017 | Updated: 07:57 GMT, 2 February 2017 371 shares
